                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6684" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">EPSM-0654</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">7798 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">以“绣”为媒，匠心筑梦——江再红的非遗匠人创业之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Take “Embroidery” as the Medium and Build up Dreams with Ingenuity——Jiang Zaihong’s Road of Starting a Business on Intangible Cultural Heritage</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">易锐，罗恺君，李馨，刘桑桑，张士杰，常江，张啸宇</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">湘潭大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">湖南再红湘绣有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">文化、体育和娱乐业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">21 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">匠人创业；非遗保护与传承；品牌叙事；创业生态系统</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Artisan Entrepreneurship; ICH Protection and Inheritance; Brand Narrative; Entrepreneurial Ecosystem </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">近年来，随着国潮文化的热度兴起和数字技术的广泛应用，越来越多的传统手工艺匠人开始尝试推广非遗手工艺产品，在品牌建立和市场销售方面取得成效。匠人创业成为带动减贫增收、彰显文化自信、促进非遗活态传承和赋能乡村振兴的重要途径。作为湖南省湘绣产业的领军企业，再红湘绣自1991年创办以来，积极探索非物质文化遗产的生产性传承道路。本案例分析了国家级非遗湘绣代表性传承人江再红的创业驱动因素，揭示了以技术磨练来塑造价值、以品牌叙事实现传播价值的匠人创业过程，同时进一步探讨了以再红湘绣为核心的创业生态系统构建思路。该案例对于非遗相关企业和传统手工匠人的文化创业实践具有一定启示和借鉴作用。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In recent years, with the rising of national culture and the wide application of digital technology, more and more traditional craftsmen started to try to promote intangible-heritage handicrafts, which had achieved success in brand establishment and marketing.Artisan entrepreneurship has become an important way to promote poverty reduction, income increase, cultural confidence manifestation, the dynamic transmission of intangible cultural heritage and rural revitalization. As a leading enterprise in Hunan embroidery industry, Zaihong Jiang embroidery has been actively exploring the path of productive inheritance of intangible cultural heritage since it was founded in 1991.This case analyses the drives of starting a business of Jiang Zaihong, a craftsman of intangible cultural heritage, uncovering the process of shaping the value by technical training and realizing the value communication by brand establishment. At the same time, it further discusses the construction of the entrepreneurial ecosystem with Zaihong Jiang embroidery as the core. It could provide enlightenment and referential significance for the workable intangible cultural heritage enterprises and the cultural entrepreneurship practice of the traditional craftsmen.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《创业管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">非遗匠人创业的概念与驱动因素；文化创业与非遗匠人创业过程；品牌叙事理论；创业生态系统</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-10</td>
                            </tr>
